Serialize Extension
===

提供了一些解决Inspector面板序列化抽象类过于冗杂的方案

- [序列化抽象类和接口](#serialize-extension_1.1)
- [使用属性代理字段的赋值](#serialize-extension_1.2)
- [控制字段在Inspector面板为只读](#serialize-extension_1.3)

## 序列化抽象类和接口 <a id="serialize-extension_1.1"></a>

通常情况下，我们会使用Unity的`[SerializeReference]`特性来在`Inspector`面板对抽象字段进行序列化操作，缺点可能就是需要为脚本提供一些Editor函数来为抽象字段决定真正的类型
~~~ csharp
public interface IPerson { }

[Serializable]
public class Teacher : IPerson 
{
    [SerializeField] int m_teachID;
}

[Serializable]
public class Student : IPerson 
{ 
    [SerializeField] string m_name;
}

public class Test : MonoBehaviour
{
    [SerializeReference] IPerson peopel;

    [ContextMenu("Add Student")]
    private void AddStudent() {
        peopel = new Student();
    }

    [ContextMenu("Add Teacher")]
    public void AddTeacher() {
        peopel = new Teacher();
    }
}
~~~
![image](https://github.com/ahiwjhb/Unity-Inspector-/blob/master/src/01.png)

![image](https://github.com/ahiwjhb/Unity-Inspector-/blob/master/src/02.png)

使用`[SerializeExtension]`特性可以在`Inspector`面板添加选择框来去除给脚本添加的Editor代码
~~~ csharp
public class Test : MonoBehaviour
{
    [SerializeExtension]
    [SerializeReference] IPerson peopel;
}
~~~
![image](https://github.com/ahiwjhb/Unity-Inspector-/blob/master/src/03.png)

## 使用属性代理字段的赋值 <a id=#serialize-extension_1.2></a>
有时候我们需要对`Inspector`面板传入的值做一些校验或者是特殊的处理，可以在使用`[SerializeExtension]`特性时选择传入`proxyPropertyName`参数来实现对字段赋值时调用特定属性来代理赋值。`proxyPropertyName`为属性名称的字符串
~~~ csharp
public class Test : MonoBehaviour
{
    [SerializeExtension(proxyPropertyName: nameof(Health))]
    [SerializeField] int m_health;

    public int Health {
        get => m_health;
        set => m_health = mathf.clamp(value, 0, 100);
    }
}
~~~
![image](https://github.com/ahiwjhb/Unity-Inspector-/blob/master/src/04.png)
![image](https://github.com/ahiwjhb/Unity-Inspector-/blob/master/src/05.png)

## 控制字段在Inspector面板为只读 <a id=serialize-extension_1.3></a>
在使用`[SerializeExtension]`特性时选择传入`canWrite`参数来实现字段在`Inspector`面板上是否可以修改
~~~ csharp
[Serializable]
public class Student : IPerson 
{ 
    [SerializeExtension(canWrite: false)]
    [SerializeField] string m_name = "ABC";
}

public class Test : MonoBehaviour
{
    [SerializeExtension]
    [SerializeReference] IPerson peopel;

    [SerializeField] int a = 10;

    [SerializeExtension(canWrite: false)]
    [SerializeField] int b = 20;
}
~~~
